nodes.name: CubeRadiance
nodes.description: Compute cubemap radiance or irradiance and generate a cubemap with optional mipmaps

parameters.name: size
parameters.description: Size of the output cubemap face width in pixels.

parameters.name: sampleCount
parameters.description: The samples count used for the blur. The more samplem the higher quality.

nodes.name: ChannelPacker

nodes.name: Lens
nodes.description: Deforms the source using a lens computation with an optionnal vignette shading.

parameters.name: vignette
parameters.description: Vignette shading: Corners get darker. 0 to disable vignette.

nodes.name: Distance
nodes.description: Generate a signed distance field from a black and white source image.

nodes.name: Multiplex
nodes.description: Route one input into the output. This choice can be propagated to further nodes.

parameters.name: multiplexer
parameters.description: Input selection passed thru the output.
